<subSubSection pageId="9" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="9.[707,1194,194,879]" pageId="9">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[731,855,805,826]" pageId="9">Etymology.</emphasis>
T h e t r i v i a l n a m e 
<emphasis box="[1096,1193,805,826]" italics="true" pageId="9">p ro l a t u s</emphasis>
